nvl(hier.apc,'unas') APC, nvl(hier.class,'unas') Class, nvl(hier.line,'unas') Line, nvl(hier.family,'unas') Family, nvl(hier.technology,'unas') Technology, nvl(hier.sbu,'unas') SBU, 'false' "ACTIVE", 'false' "integration_in_scope"
from apps.mtl_system_items_b msi, oc.mot_chs_sf_itm_his his, apps.c_fnd_lookups_v flvv, (SELECT mc.segment1 apc, mc.segment2 class, mc.segment3 line, mc.segment4 family, mc.segment5 technology, mc.segment6 sbu, ffv.description apc_desc, mic.organization_id, mic.inventory_item_id FROM apps.mtl_category_sets mcs, apps.mtl_item_categories mic, apps.mtl_categories mc, apps.fnd_flex_values_vl ffv WHERE mcs.category_set_name = 'PROD HIER' AND mic.category_set_id = mcs.category_set_id AND mc.category_id = mic.category_id AND ffv.flex_value = mc.segment1 AND ffv.flex_value_set_id = 1007712) hier
where 1=1 and msi.organization_id = 102 AND msi.inventory_item_id = HIS.INVENTORY_ITEM_ID AND msi.item_type = flvv.lookup_code AND flvv.lookup_type in ( 'ITEM_TYPE') AND hier.inventory_item_id(+) = msi.inventory_item_id AND hier.organization_id(+)=msi.organization_id AND msi.inventory_item_id not in ( SELECT msi.inventory_item_id FROM apps.mtl_system_items_b msi, apps.c_fnd_lookups_v flvv, apps.c_fnd_lookups_v flvv1 ,apps.c_fnd_lookups_v CFV_ITEM_STATUS ,apps.c_fnd_lookups_v cfv_item_type WHERE 1=1 AND flvv1.lookup_type = 'C_SF_ORG_ITEM' AND msi.organization_id = flvv1.description AND msi.organization_id IN ( SELECT to_number(flv.description) FROM apps.c_fnd_lookups_v flv WHERE flv.lookup_type = 'C_SF_ORG_ITEM' ) AND inventory_item_status_code = cfv_item_status.attribute1 and cfv_item_status.lookup_type = 'C_SF_ITMPR_PKG_VALUES' AND cfv_item_status.attribute_category = 'C_SF_ITEM_STATUS' AND msi.item_type = cfv_item_type.attribute1 and cfv_item_type.lookup_type ='C_SF_ITMPR_PKG_VALUES' AND cfv_item_type.attribute_category ='C_SF_ITEM_TYPES' AND NVL (msi.default_shipping_org, 0) != 236 AND msi.item_type = flvv.lookup_code AND flvv.lookup_type = 'ITEM_TYPE' ) order by msi.segment1 )
